## 1. Project Overview

**Project Name**: AI Smart Expense Manager & Money Coach  
**Version**: 1.0  
**Team**: Computer Science Students  
**Duration**: 3-4 weeks  
**Status**: Ready to Build

### 1.1 What This App Does

A simple web app that:
- Imports your bank transactions automatically.
- Categorizes expenses using AI.
- Tracks your budgets and sends alerts.
- Finds hidden subscriptions.
- Gives personalized saving tips using AI.

### 1.2 Who Uses This App

- Students and freshers with first salary.
- Young professionals (Рѓ╣15k-60k/month).
- Anyone who wants to save money but doesn't know where to start.

### 1.3 Key Problem Being Solved

Most people have Рѓ╣20,000-50,000 per month but don't know where it goes. They want simple, clear guidance on how to save moreРђћnot just charts and numbers.

